OL,5, Cecil Taylor, BBC News NI's first TV   
OL,6, reporter, has died at the age of 96.   
OL,8,FHe began his career at the BBC at the  
OL,9,Fsame moment BBC TV news bulletins were 
OL,10,Fborn in 1955.                          
OL,12,FTributes have been paid by many former 
OL,13,Fcolleagues, who described him as a     
OL,14,Fsolid and valued news pioneer.         
OL,16,FDon Anderson, who worked with him at   
OL,17,Fthe BBC for many years, said Mr Taylor 
OL,18,Fwas a brave journalist who "began the  
OL,19,FBBC's journey towards proper impartial 
OL,20,Fjournalism here".                      
